content.html: Deleting Slack, LinkedIn, Twitter, emails from my phone has soothed my brain so much the past few days. Good reminder that you don’t need to be connected 24/7 and that’s okay! It’s noisy online sometimes, its okay to rest. 🫶🏻
content.value:
Deleting Slack, LinkedIn, Twitter, emails from my phone has soothed my brain so much the past few days. 

Good reminder that you don’t need to be connected 24/7 and that’s okay! It’s noisy online sometimes, its okay to rest. 🫶🏻
